column2: SELECT TOP # s.SpecObjID,    s.z,    L.ew,    L.sigma,    L.height,    dbo.fCosmoDl(s.z),    wave,    restWave,    so.mag_# into mydb.SFRnoz from SpecPhoto as s,    SpecLine  as L,   SpecObjAll as so    WHERE s.specClass = #      AND L.lineID = #      AND L.ew > #      AND L.height > #       AND L.specObjID = s.specObjID     AND so.specObjID = s.specObjID
